race.description: Auto Owls Bentley W.a. Bred Country Cup H
race.comment: DANCING DAWN (1) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 4 lengths (21.54) at Cannington. Rates on top again. OUR BENSON (8) got around 509m in a swift 29.57 when winning a OPEN at this track last start. Expecting another bold showing. TRANSCENDENT (6) struggled for best form latest, finishing 8th (31.60) in a Grade 4/5 at Cannington. Goes very well at course and distance boasting four wins. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Cannot be taken lightly. INCREDIBLE KING (4) is another with top-three prospects.
